{"tid":2280994,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"居大陸港人本月23日起回港可豁免隔離 以隱形傳播鏈及流感為由推算第四次爆發","createTime":"2020-11-11T02:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T02:55:31.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d47a834a7f35a82334e6021026c974cbbc895841","tid":2280994,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T02:17:26.000Z","msg":"居內地港人本月23日起可豁免回港強制檢疫<br />\n<br />\n政府公布，獲政務司司長豁免的居於內地港人，本月23日起，持有兩地認可的新型冠狀病毒陰性檢測結果，回港後可豁免強制檢疫14日的安排。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局長陳肇始表示，本港過去一星期有多宗不明源頭個案，社區仍有隱形傳播鏈，過去7天不明源頭個案平均數，由月初0.3升至0.6，本地個案亦由0.4升至1.1，不容忽視，要提高警覺，一旦鬆懈，可能出現第四波疫情，加上冬季流感，疫情可能較第三波嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2365707\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2365707&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=12f987aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2365707</a>"},{"pid":"ac539092e29d73074718562d4f2740d7564a971b","tid":2280994,"uid":8014,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T02:19:53.000Z","msg":"咁唔洗大灣區投票啦 反正可以免檢疫落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c455dfa03da11a4fadac8b82017a7728ba452cc1","tid":2280994,"uid":44171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T02:22:35.000Z","msg":"香港咁危險，仲黎做咩？"},{"pid":"2cb4f5a556ce2c00f3d32e539b60f4b65c38c3ec","tid":2280994,"uid":87471,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T02:23:36.000Z","msg":"r撚爆頭，前一句話唔可以放鬆<br />\n之後一句就係大陸落黎免檢疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2765ceaa883fd1c551d40163c64e13c958c9112","tid":2280994,"uid":74361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T02:24:30.000Z","msg":"驚咩？"},{"pid":"0101ca419ad7eb9aa06caf0bdf5a7d2fdedd14f5","tid":2280994,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re